findings.title: Role owner has authority to withdraw ether
findings.description: The role owner has the authority to withdraw ether from the contract at any point of time.

findings.title: Missing Range Check for Input Variable
findings.description: The input variable lacks a range check, which can lead to potential security issues.

findings.title: Missing zero address validation
findings.description: The variable uniRouter is initialized with the value of PANCAKESWAP_ROUTER_ADDRESS, at the time of construction. At that point of time PANCAKESWAP_ROUTER_ADDRESS is also zero address.
